"title": "2048: Jesus Christ, love of",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "2048",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>Jesus Christ's total giving of himself, shown supremely in his obedient suffering and death on the cross, reveals God's amazing love for sinners. It continues to motivate and inspire Christians today.</p>\n<h2>The supreme quality of Jesus Christ's love</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph3:17-Eph3:19\">EPH 3:17–3:19</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom8:35\">ROM 8:35</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom8:38-Rom8:39\">ROM 8:38–8:39</a></p>\n<h3>It caused him to leave his eternal glory</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor8:9\">2CO 8:9</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Phil2:6-Phil2:8\">PHP 2:6–2:8</a></p>\n<h3>It moved him to give his life for others</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1John3:16\">1JN 3:16</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John10:11\">JHN 10:11</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John10:14-John10:15\">JHN 10:14–10:15</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John15:13\">JHN 15:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph5:2\">EPH 5:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev1:5\">REV 1:5</a></p>\n<h3>He loves sinners</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke23:34\">LUK 23:34</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke13:34\">LUK 13:34</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt23:37\">MAT 23:37</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke23:43\">LUK 23:43</a></p>\n<h3>He loves each believer</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Thess2:13\">2TH 2:13</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John10:3-John10:5\">JHN 10:3–10:5</a></p>\n<h2>Examples of Jesus Christ's love</h2>\n<h3>His compassion for the needy</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt9:36\">MAT 9:36</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark6:34\">MRK 6:34</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt14:14\">MAT 14:14</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt15:32\">MAT 15:32</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark8:1-Mark8:2\">MRK 8:1–8:2</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke7:13\">LUK 7:13</a></p>\n<h3>His love for children</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt19:13-Matt19:15\">MAT 19:13–19:15</a> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark10:13-Mark10:16\">MRK 10:13–10:16</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke18:15-Luke18:17\">LUK 18:15–18:17</a></p>\n<h3>His love for his mother</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/John19:26-John19:27\">JHN 19:26–19:27</a></p>\n<h3>His love for his followers</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/John13:1\">JHN 13:1</a></strong> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John11:1-John11:7\">JHN 11:1–11:7</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John11:17-John11:22\">JHN 11:17–11:22</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John11:32-John11:44\">JHN 11:32–11:44</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John13:23\">JHN 13:23</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John20:2\">JHN 20:2</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John21:7\">JHN 21:7</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John21:20\">JHN 21:20</a></p>\n<h2>Jesus Christ's love stems from the Father</h2>\n<h3>He receives the Father's love</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/John3:35\">JHN 3:35</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt17:5\">MAT 17:5</a> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark9:7\">MRK 9:7</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke9:35\">LUK 9:35</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark1:11\">MRK 1:11</a> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt3:17\">MAT 3:17</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke3:22\">LUK 3:22</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John5:20\">JHN 5:20</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John14:31\">JHN 14:31</a></p>\n<h3>His love reveals the Father's love</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom5:8\">ROM 5:8</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John3:16\">JHN 3:16</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph2:4-Eph2:5\">EPH 2:4–2:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1John4:9-1John4:10\">1JN 4:9–4:10</a></p>\n<h2>Jesus Christ's love motivates the church</h2>\n<h3>His love indwells believers</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/John17:26\">JHN 17:26</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John15:9-John15:10\">JHN 15:9–15:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gal2:20\">GAL 2:20</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Tim1:14\">1TI 1:14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1John4:12\">1JN 4:12</a></p>\n<h3>His love disciplines believers</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev3:19\">REV 3:19</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb12:5-Heb12:6\">HEB 12:5–12:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov3:11-Prov3:12\">PRO 3:11–3:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev3:9\">REV 3:9</a></p>\n<h3>His love inspires authentic Christian attitudes</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/John13:34-John13:35\">JHN 13:34–13:35</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev19:18\">LEV 19:18</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut6:5\">DEU 6:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt5:43-Matt5:44\">MAT 5:43–5:44</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt22:35-Matt22:39\">MAT 22:35–22:39</a> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark12:28-Mark12:31\">MRK 12:28–12:31</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke10:25-Luke10:27\">LUK 10:25–10:27</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke6:27\">LUK 6:27</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John15:12\">JHN 15:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1John3:10\">1JN 3:10</a></p>\n<h3>His love inspires Christian marriage</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph5:25\">EPH 5:25</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph5:28-Eph5:30\">EPH 5:28–5:30</a></p>\n<h3>His love inspires a desire for spiritual gifts</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor14:1\">1CO 14:1</a></strong></p>\n<h3>His love motivates Christians to live for God</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor5:14-2Cor5:15\">2CO 5:14–5:15</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom8:37\">ROM 8:37</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor16:14\">1CO 16:14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col2:2\">COL 2:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Thess1:3\">1TH 1:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb10:24\">HEB 10:24</a></p>",
